        "title": "fix(control-ui): honor verbose level for tool expansion",
        "body": "Fixes #49944.\n\n## Summary\n\n- Preserve the effective `chat.history.verboseLevel` returned by the gateway in Control UI state.\n- Use `chatVerboseLevel === \"full\"` to initialize chat tool-card expansion through the existing `autoExpandToolCalls` rendering path.\n- Clear stale verbose-level state on session switches and unauthorized history loads alongside the existing thinking-level state.\n- Add focused regression coverage for history loading and app render wiring.\n\n## Scope\n\nThis is intentionally limited to Control UI state/render plumbing. It does not change gateway session metadata, tool-card manual toggles, or the existing expansion-state helper behavior.\n\n## Validation\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.unit-ui.config.ts ui/src/ui/controllers/chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.assistant-avatar.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/chat/tool-expansion-state.test.ts`\n- `pnpm exec oxfmt --check --threads=1 ui/src/ui/controllers/chat.ts ui/src/ui/app-view-state.ts ui/src/ui/app.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.helpers.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.ts ui/src/ui/controllers/chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.assistant-avatar.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-render.helpers.node.test.ts CHANGELOG.md`\n- `pnpm check:changed`\n\n## Screenshots\n\nNo live screenshot attached. This patch changes the initial `open` state passed to native `<details>` tool cards; focused controller/render tests cover the behavior.\n\n## AI-assisted disclosure\n\nAI-assisted PR prepared with Codex. I reviewed the code paths touched, kept the change scoped to #49944, and ran the validation listed above.",
